reviewText: Both films are great. PG is such a good movie for its comedic effect on the audience, and WBAZ is emotional at times and fun at others.
Great deal for two really good movies.  We bought a Zoo is one of my favorites...very sad though.  Parental guidance is so funny!
Great deal on good movies. I bought these as stocking stuffers for Christmas this past year.  Mom was very pleased!

When I saw your illustrated picture - I thought I would be receiving two separate movies - packaged separately so that I could give them as gifts to two different people.  Instead I was stuck with one gift.  Wasn't happy.
